8.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/8823690" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2526065&amp;issue-id=354832&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=J+Rheumatol&amp;title=Risk+factors+for+Pneumocystis+carinii+pneumonia+in+patients+with+polymyositis/dermatomyositis+or+systemic+lupus+erythematosus&amp;author=A+Kadoya&amp;author=J+Okada&amp;author=Y+Iikuni&amp;author=H+Kondo&amp;volume=23&amp;issue=7&amp;publication_year=1996&amp;pages=1186-8&amp;pmid=8823690&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2526065&amp;issue-id=354832&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="CR9">9. <span class="element-citation">Huang YC, Lin YT, Yang YH, Wang SJ, Yang CM, Chiang BL. Acute lupus pneumonitis mimicking pulmonary tuberculosis: a case report. <span><span class="ref-journal">J Microbiol Immunol Infect. </span>2001;<span class="ref-vol">34</span>(2):143\xe2\x80\x936.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/11456361" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2526065&amp;issue-id=354832&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=J+Microbiol+Immunol+Infect&amp;title=Acute+lupus+pneumonitis+mimicking+pulmonary+tuberculosis:+a+case+report&amp;author=YC+Huang&amp;author=YT+Lin&amp;author=YH+Yang&amp;author=SJ+Wang&amp;author=CM+Yang&amp;volume=34&amp;issue=2&amp;publication_year=2001&amp;pages=143-6&amp;pmid=11456361&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2526065&amp;issue-id=354832&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div></div></div></div><!--